<text>
    <body>
        <div1 type="summary">
            <p><add hand="#barker">Authorizing suit against Stephen F. Austin to collect note.</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p>This Shall authorise and empower <persName>Pierre Alexander Laforge
attorney</persName> in fact for the <persName>heirs of Pierre Antoine Laforge Decease</persName>&#8212;-
Or his <persName>Executors </persName>or <persName>Administrators </persName>to ask, demand sue for and
receive one thousand five hundred and twenty dollars which is due
from <persName>Stephen F. Austin</persName> on a note bearing date the <date when="1819-01-30">30th January
1819</date> and payable on the <date when="1821-02-01">first day of February 1821</date> which said note
I have this day given into the hands of said <persName>Laforge </persName>for his own
proper use and benefit&#8212;</p>

<p>Witness my hand and Seal this <date when="1820-06-13">13th June 1820</date></p>

<p><persName>George Tennille </persName>   [Rubric]</p>

        </div1>
    </body>
